		<title>ATFX Connect获得Cyber Essentials Plus认证</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/zh-hans/company-news/atfx-connect-cyber-essentials-plus-certification</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 09:00:11 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[公司新闻]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[ATFX Connect]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[最近的新闻]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.atfx.com/?p=47345</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[ATFX Connect作为ATFX的机构业务品牌，成功获得 Cyber Essentials Plus 认证 [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.atfxconnect.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="font-weight: 400;">ATFX Connect</span></a><span data-contrast="auto">作为</span><span data-contrast="auto">ATFX</span><span data-contrast="auto">的机构业务品牌，成功获得</span><span data-contrast="auto"> Cyber Essentials Plus </span><span data-contrast="auto">认证，彰显了其在</span><span data-contrast="auto"> IT </span><span data-contrast="auto">基础设施安全和严格的网络安全措施方面的承诺。</span><span data-ccp-props="{}"> </span></p>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">Cyber Essentials Plus </span><span data-contrast="auto">是由英国政府支持的网络安全认证，要求通过独立的技术审查，以验证企业是否具备抵御常见网络威胁（如恶意软件、网络钓鱼攻击和黑客入侵）的能力。该认证由</span><span data-contrast="auto">IASME</span><span data-contrast="auto">负责管理，相比标准版</span><span data-contrast="auto">Cyber Essentials</span><span data-contrast="auto">，具备更高的安全保障级别。</span><span data-ccp-props="{}"> </span></p>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">该认证是由</span><span data-contrast="auto">Bulletproof</span><span data-contrast="auto">颁发，并经过</span><span data-contrast="auto">IASME</span><span data-contrast="auto">审核，表明</span><span data-contrast="auto">ATFX Connect</span><span data-contrast="auto">的网络防御体系经过严格测试，并符合行业标准，有效抵御基于通用工具的网络威胁。认证评估涵盖了</span> <span data-contrast="auto">防火墙配置、访问控制、恶意软件防护及系统补丁管理等关键安全措施，确保其网络安全防护符合最佳行业实践。</span><span data-ccp-props="{}"> </span></p>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">对于机构客户而言，网络安全是建立信任和保障运营完整性的关键。</span><span data-contrast="auto">ATFX Connect </span><span data-contrast="auto">获得</span><span data-contrast="auto"> Cyber Essentials Plus </span><span data-contrast="auto">认证，进一步展示了其在保护客户数据、防范网络风险以及维护安全交易环境方面的坚定承诺。</span><span data-ccp-props="{}"> </span></p>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">在竞争激烈的机构交易市场，强大的网络安全措施是关键竞争优势。</span><span data-contrast="auto">ATFX Connect </span><span data-contrast="auto">通过获得</span><span data-contrast="auto"> Cyber Essentials Plus </span><span data-contrast="auto">认证，不仅符合行业标准，更在市场中脱颖而出，彰显其在保障客户利益方面的前瞻性安全策略。</span><span data-ccp-props="{}"> </span></p>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">随着网络安全威胁不断升级，</span><span data-contrast="auto">ATFX Connect </span><span data-contrast="auto">将持续优化安全体系，确保符合行业标准，为机构客户提供稳健且安全的交易平台。</span><span data-ccp-props="{}"> </span></p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
